{"tid":1761793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警撤離後兩人牽手離開理大","createTime":"2019-11-29T06:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T10:45:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":191,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"9f647fba9bc95a30a493a92896caec8f44dc24fa","tid":1761793,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191129/_2019112913444155474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191129%2F_2019112913444155474.jpg&h=9557b2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方中午解封理工大學，將校園交回校方管理。調查人員撤走後，一對戴黑色口罩的男女中午牽手離開理大，但兩人並無透露自己是否連日在校園內留守的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n理大於中午取回校園控制權後，一批保安員連隨進入校內。校方亦發出聲明指，校園情況仍存在不安全因素，而且清理、盤點及修復工作需時，故此校方表示，校園仍需關閉，只限校方授權人士進入，直至另行通告為止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191129/_2019112913444280614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191129%2F_2019112913444280614.jpg&h=b08ada79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1149488/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%BD%E6%89%8B%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7-%E7%84%A1%E9%80%8F%E9%9C%B2%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d4dd6d5806660afe26b5af5061104237a5c89b95","tid":1761793,"uid":328890,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f99264f83fcb9a6e026b48e6ca9a9f1b1e118ba3","tid":1761793,"uid":50670,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"反正無人想知啦屌"},{"pid":"aed6ebc8e929351ff9494401726bbaf375490687","tid":1761793,"uid":328890,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0